msgstr ""
"Sistemi MacOS: `TunnelBlick <https://tunnelblick.net/>`_ oppure il `Client "
"Ufficiale <https://openvpn.net/client-connect-vpn-for-mac-os/>`_"

#: ../../openvpn_roadwarrior.rst:169 e81d581794ff4a878b7bc8311602db78
